lion</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>2003</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>2010</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>up 51.5%</p></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\" colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tr-strong\">COMPANIES NEARING $1 TRILLION IN MARKET CAPITALIZATION</span></p></td><td align=\"center\"><p><br/></p></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\"><p>Meta Platforms <a href=\"reuters://REALTIME/Verb=FullQuote/ric=FB.O\" data-type=\"ric\" data-ric=\"FB.O\" translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">FB.O</a></p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>$919.54 billion</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>2004</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>2012</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>up ~21%</p></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\"><p>Nvidia Corp <a href=\"reuters://REALTIME/Verb=FullQuote/ric=NVDA.O\" data-type=\"ric\" data-ric=\"NVDA.O\" translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">NVDA.O</a></p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>$795.65 billion</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>1993</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>1999</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>up 143.8%</p></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\"><p>Berkshire Hathaway <a href=\"reuters://REALTIME/Verb=FullQuote/ric=BRKa.N\" data-type=\"ric\" data-ric=\"BRKa.N\" translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">BRKa.N</a> </p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>$634.79 billion</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>1839</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>1980</p></td><td align=\"center\"><p>up 22.9%</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><div class=\"tr-resource-ref\" id=\"g39706b61-68e2-4339-bed4-2beac02c3696\"><div class=\"tr-image\"><div class=\"tr-image-components\"><img src=\"https://fingfx.thomsonreuters.com/gfx/mkt/lgpdwojxovo/Pasted%20image%201639053779098.png\" data-internal-src=\"https://rp.cp.dtc.reuint.com/Apps/NewsServices/images?apiKey=95a7d790-a5d1-4907-9c62-c9d7a1d29f80&amp;type=base64Url&amp;id=aHR0cHM6Ly9maW5nZngudGhvbXNvbnJldXRlcnMuY29tL2dmeC9ta3QvbGdwZHdvanhvdm8vUGFzdGVkJTIwaW1hZ2UlMjAxNjM5MDUzNzc5MDk4LnBuZw==&amp;storyId=urn:newsml:reuters.com:20211209:nL4N2SU2M8:1&amp;key=c061f34b35c03f11b4bcbbc05c8abd86fcc8